osti; <span class=\"highlighted-text\">have to</span> u sadašnjosti.</p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Have to</span> je časnije od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">must</span>.</p>"],"text":"<p>Шта је разлика између <span class=\"highlighted-text\">must</span> и <span class=\"highlighted-text\">have to</span>?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Must</span> je unutrašnje; <span class=\"highlighted-text\">have to</span> je spoljašnje.</p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Long-term goals</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Future plans</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Extra duties</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Kako se zove posao koji osoba mora da radi svakog dana?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Daily tasks</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">You are late unless you hurry.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">You are late unless you will hurry.</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">You will be late unless you hurried.</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja rečenica koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">unless</span> pravilno?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">You will be late unless you hurry.</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p>Raditi nekoliko sati</p>","<p>Raditi od kuće</p>","<p>Raditi vrlo sporo</p>"],"text":"<p>Šta znači <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to work overtime</span>?</p>","answer":"<p>Rad na prekovremenim satima</p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Job rotation</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Time tracking</span></p>","<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Career growth</span></p>"],"text":"<p>Šta se zove ravnoteža između posla i privatnog života?</p>","answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Work-life balance</span></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Seriou